{"tid":2381013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「椰子」邱文勁獲不同光譜政治人物撰寫求情信 將於3月判刑","createTime":"2021-01-26T09:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T05:35:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":67,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"992e5198212305d3ad8459ae6f2adb7d05ffa75e","tid":2381013,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T09:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eRijDLnMnP22VIY74orssik6MOw=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7YVIYNOZGJHWZL7PNKT5CVN3GE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeRijDLnMnP22VIY74orssik6MOw%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7YVIYNOZGJHWZL7PNKT5CVN3GE.jpg&h=9b49753b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反修例運動期間，群眾前往香港國際機場示威，爆發衝突。其間有警員驅散示威者時聲稱遇襲，一度拔槍示警，事後多人被捕。當中社區主任邱文勁與25歲港鐵維修員於開審前承認暴動罪，還柙至今日求情。邱透過代表大狀指，今次判刑後將喪失各級議會被選舉權利，對熱心公共事務的他而言是極大的打擊。辯方又指，港鐵維修員患有過度活躍症及亞氏保加症，當日受警方行為刺激情緒而犯案，至今已還柙近500日，望法庭輕判。法官郭啟安下令二人繼續還柙，等候同案另外兩名被告的案件審結，預料今年3月判刑。<br />\n<br />\n代表首被告邱文勁的大律師劉偉聰指，被告甫投身社會便擔任社區主任及區議員助理，亦有參選區議會，顯示他熱衷公共事務。今次判刑後，被告將依法喪失各級選舉的被選舉權利，對被告而言是極大的打擊。<br />\n<br />\n眾多求情信透露，被告於大學就讀經濟系，在學期間已非常關心社會，大學三年級時參與反高鐵運動，後因情緒問題而輟學。另有多個區議員亦為被告撰寫求情信，光譜由和理非至本土派，均顯示被告品格良好正直。被告母親則指，等兒子出獄後，會全力支持被告，母親亦希望被告好好反省，明白未來的路仍很漫長。<br />\n<br />\n至於案件細節，辯方指人群在玻璃屋聚集至警方驅散期間，維時短速；而事件在室內發生，不易擴散。被告犯案時沒有遮掩面容，顯示被告沒有預謀參與事件，當時只是希望參與機場集會，沒有打算使用暴力。<br />\n<br />\n被告自知不會獲得全數三分一刑期扣減，惟希望法庭考慮到被告只是深思考慮結果，給予他四分一扣減、或給予最大的折扣以至最低的量刑起點，讓他早日重投社會事務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210126/IIMU7P24WVBG5FK6WASTDMHNFQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210126%2FIIMU7P24WVBG5FK6WASTDMHNFQ%2F&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv9VSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=3ff7b849\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210126%2FIIMU7P24WVBG5FK6WASTDMHNFQ%2F&h=73688519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210126/IIMU7P24WVBG5FK6WASTDMHNFQ/</a>"},{"pid":"86560658736c0d7f272e73d1858582d76ec0f5d1","tid":2381013,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T09:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed480a2625858bb3f7cb84e6503ea79e9a669814","tid":2381013,"uid":15697,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T09:40:03.000Z","msg":"唉椰子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢真係好勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49dca98e652aac487883b1603c94d766734eaea","tid":2381013,"uid":50931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T09:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c69323f9c7685876e811f4539371c2e079263c","tid":2381013,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T09:45:25.000Z","msg":"椰子巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd64da420c4794da0068469c3c7a020225e0122c","tid":2381013,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T10:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eefd52f6125fee4fc746826b3278f43ef765eaa8","tid":2381013,"uid":1241,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T10:35:17.000Z","msg":"椰子是無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a975258f15b4a4fd2d2606720c719426b21c7302","tid":2381013,"uid":284429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci